<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>13</hymn_number>
<title>Chis čs im anumpa hoka ∆≤IT13</title>
<time_sig>8.7.8.7.4.7.</time_sig>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chis čs im anumpa hoka
 Okla mom čt ho haklo:
 Nan uŐĪha k čt  člhtah čshke;
 Im anumpa ho haklo;
.    
     Chis čs ok čt
 Pi Okchalinchi yoke.

[V2]
 Okla ilb čsha pia h čt
 Chis čs holitopa yaŐĪ
 Iloh iŐĪ yimmi pullashke;
 H čpiŐĪ nukhaŐĪklo yoke.
.    
     Chis čs ok čt
 Pi Okchalinchi yoke.

[V3]
 Chitokaka Chis čs oka
 Iloh im antiashke;
 H čpi Okchalinchi yoka;
 Eho holitoblashke.
.    
     Chis čs ok čt
 Pi Okchalinchi yoke.

[V4]
 Nanta'k ona e toba wa,
 Pilli pulla chiŐĪ hoke;
 Chis čs iloh iŐĪ yimmi cha,
 Pi okchaŐĪya pullashke
.    
     Chis čs ok čt
 Pi Okchalinchi yoke.

[V5]
 Chis čs ik iŐĪ yimmo tukm čt
 Luak chito ia he;
 Chis čs aŐĪ iŐĪ yimmi tukm čt
 ∆≤ba yoka ia he:
.    
     Chis čs ok čt
 Pi Okchalinchi yoke.

[V6]
 Okla h čpi moma hok čt
 ∆≤ba aholitopa
 Pit iloh ahni pullashke;
 Aiachukmaka yoke:
.    
     Chis čs oka
 Eho pesa pullashke.</lyrics>
</song>